        "numItems": 6,
        "totalMarks": 100,
        "structureNotes": "Section A: 2 compulsory scenario items. Section B: 4 scenario items, answer 3. Each item = 20 marks. 6 scenarios drawn from the 5 EoC. 70% weighting overall. Duration 2h30.",
