  "scoringCriteria": {
    "rules": [
      "Calculation items/tasks are allocated method marks, determined by the appropriate stages in the solution.",
      "The correct final answer in a calculation is allocated a separate accuracy mark.",
      "Marks are allocated for correct diagrams/graphs drawn and accuracy of measurements within them.",
      "Projects and practical activities are scored per the SBA Guidelines Scoring Rubrics, not this method/accuracy scheme.",
      "Omission of essential working results in loss of marks; learners must show working.",
      "Candidates may use silent non-programmable scientific calculators; premature approximation before the final step loses the accuracy mark.",
      "Use 3.14, 3.142 or the calculator value of pi unless the item specifies otherwise."
    ]
  },
